    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div class="note note-success">            <p>记录 Github 学习相关内容</p>          </div><h2 id="1-置顶仓库"><a href="#1-置顶仓库" class="headerlink" title="1. 置顶仓库"></a>1. 置顶仓库</h2><ol><li>在想置顶的仓库，点击<span class="label label-danger">Pin(置顶)</span></li></ol><p><img src="/mason_blog/PixPin_2026-03-05_12-46-26.png" alt="Repositories"></p><ol start="2"><li>返回<span class="label label-danger">Profile(个人资料)</span>就可以看到仓库被顶置，显示<span class="label label-danger">Pinned(已置顶)</span></li></ol><p><img src="/mason_blog/PixPin_2026-03-05_12-47-42.png" alt="Profile"></p>]]></content>
    
    
